I love reading all the comments.

00:01:33.100 --> 00:01:35.466
-We really read them all.
-Really.

00:01:35.466 --> 00:01:40.866
We can't answer them all,
we can't put them all here,

00:01:40.866 --> 00:01:42.666
but we read all of them.

00:01:42.666 --> 00:01:46.300
So, send your comment because
we are going to read it.

00:01:46.300 --> 00:01:48.000
And remember, in any language.

